/*
 * ============================================================
 *   SMART HELMET — NodeMCU ESP8266
 *   Fixes: Button debounce | GPS debug | Impact+GPS alert
 * ============================================================
 *
 *  WIRING:
 *  MPU6050  SDA → GPIO4  (D2)
 *  MPU6050  SCL → GPIO5  (D1)
 *  HC-SR04  TRIG → GPIO14 (D5)
 *  HC-SR04  ECHO → GPIO12 (D6)  [1kΩ+1kΩ divider → 2.5V]
 *  GPS      TX  → GPIO13 (D7)   [GPS RX not connected]
 *  Buzzer   NPN → GPIO15 (D8)   [via 1kΩ]
 *  MQ-3     DO  → GPIO2  (D4)
 *  Button       → GPIO16 (D0)   [10kΩ pull-up to 3.3V — REQUIRED]
 *
 *  LIBRARIES (Library Manager):
 *  - Adafruit MPU6050
 *  - Adafruit Unified Sensor
 *  - TinyGPS++
 *  - Universal Arduino Telegram Bot
 *  - ArduinoJson
 *
 *  BOARD: NodeMCU 1.0 (ESP-12E Module)
 * ============================================================
 */

